text: The 2018 All-Ireland Senior Camogie Championship Final, the 87th event of its kind and the culmination of the 2018 All-Ireland Senior Camogie Championship, was played at Croke Park in Dublin on 9 September 2018. It was the third Cork–Kilkenny final in a row, and was won by Cork by one point. ==Details== ==References== 1 Category:All-Ireland Senior Camogie Championship Finals
title: 2018 All-Ireland Senior Camogie Championship Final
